WEBVTT

01:30.890 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.820 --> 01:39.500
[1998]

01:38.640 --> 01:39.400
Son, look.

01:47.759 --> 01:48.820
Anything you need?

01:49.380 --> 01:51.910
There's a parent-teacher meeting tomorrow.

01:53.310 --> 01:55.000
I can't take time off tomorrow.

01:55.000 --> 01:55.930
Do you have time?

01:56.200 --> 01:57.590
They'll dock my pay if I take time off.

01:57.590 --> 01:58.590
What do you think?

01:59.430 --> 01:59.840
Son.

01:59.960 --> 02:00.620
Look, look.

02:00.710 --> 02:02.040
Wu Song has reached Jingyang Ridge.

02:02.040 --> 02:03.500
What's on Jingyang Ridge?

02:03.790 --> 02:05.590
There's... A big tiger!

02:06.780 --> 02:07.640
It'll bite you! Bite you!

02:07.640 --> 02:08.680
Don't scare him.

02:09.550 --> 02:10.310
Your dad is just teasing you.

02:10.310 --> 02:11.640
Look, there's no tiger.

02:12.080 --> 02:12.910
Look, there's nothing here.

02:12.910 --> 02:13.630
Look. Look.

02:13.750 --> 02:14.910
It hasn't come out yet. No.

02:14.910 --> 02:15.800
He's going up.

02:16.070 --> 02:16.840
There's no tiger.

02:16.840 --> 02:18.120
Wu Song is going up the mountain.

02:18.120 --> 02:19.050
Jingyang Ridge.

02:19.079 --> 02:19.680
He's gone.

02:38.910 --> 02:41.460
[Episode 3]
[A Strange Home]

02:42.870 --> 02:43.680
Am I supposed to

02:43.680 --> 02:44.400
be inferior

02:44.560 --> 02:45.030
just because of thugs like you

02:45.030 --> 02:46.030
and those

02:46.240 --> 02:47.300
malicious rumors?

02:47.470 --> 02:48.840
Am I supposed to let someone like you

02:48.840 --> 02:50.240
who spreads lies everywhere

02:50.240 --> 02:51.360
continue doing evil,

02:51.360 --> 02:51.870
while I,

02:51.870 --> 02:53.150
a completely innocent victim,

02:53.150 --> 02:54.630
have to cower and keep my head down?

02:54.630 --> 02:56.030
-Why should I?
-Exactly.

02:56.280 --> 02:57.630
-Well said!
-That's right.

02:57.630 --> 02:58.400
This young lady

02:58.400 --> 02:59.720
was slandered for no reason.

02:59.720 --> 03:01.030
Of course she should
speak up for herself.

03:01.030 --> 03:01.830
Yes, exactly.

03:02.000 --> 03:03.240
What nonsense are you talking about?

03:03.240 --> 03:04.100
I didn't really

03:04.280 --> 03:06.280
take advantage of you back then, did I?

03:06.280 --> 03:07.240
You didn't take advantage of her,

03:07.240 --> 03:08.710
yet you dared accuse her of
being a loose woman?

03:08.710 --> 03:10.150
You should be sent to the police station!

03:10.150 --> 03:11.080
Take him away! Take him away!

03:11.080 --> 03:12.800
-To the police station!
-To the police station!

03:12.800 --> 03:14.260
You all heard that, right?

03:14.280 --> 03:16.000
Zhang Erlai admitted it himself

03:16.000 --> 03:17.470
that he tried to take advantage of me.

03:17.470 --> 03:18.680
He was the one
spreading rumors everywhere.

03:18.680 --> 03:20.150
Nothing happened between him and me!

03:20.150 --> 03:21.260
Did everyone hear that?

03:21.260 --> 03:22.120
Those were all your words!

03:22.120 --> 03:24.360
May heaven strike down
whoever spreads rumors!

03:24.360 --> 03:25.280
You bastard!

03:25.460 --> 03:27.120
Last time, I saw you had a few drinks

03:27.120 --> 03:28.030
and started boasting to others

03:28.030 --> 03:29.420
that you'd done that thing
with Xia Xiaolan.

03:29.420 --> 03:30.470
Did you say that or not?

03:30.470 --> 03:31.810
See? He said it!

03:31.840 --> 03:33.960
Take him to the police station!
Say no more.

03:33.960 --> 03:35.079
It's not true!

03:35.240 --> 03:36.710
To the police station!

03:36.710 --> 03:37.800
You pervert!

03:37.840 --> 03:39.840
Take him to the police station!

03:39.870 --> 03:41.600
Take him to the police station!

03:42.079 --> 03:43.610
Quickly, take him to the police station!

03:43.610 --> 03:44.360
To the police station!

03:44.360 --> 03:45.520
The police are here!

03:45.840 --> 03:46.970
That's Zhang Erlai.

03:47.430 --> 03:48.910
That's Zhang Erlai, right?

03:48.910 --> 03:49.470
Yes, that's him!

03:49.470 --> 03:50.079
I'm not!

03:50.360 --> 03:51.300
Still trying to deny it?

03:51.300 --> 03:51.960
All the girls in this village

03:51.960 --> 03:53.240
have been harassed by him.

03:53.240 --> 03:54.120
Still trying to deny it?

03:54.120 --> 03:54.870
That's Zhang Erlai.

03:54.870 --> 03:56.130
Enough. Stop talking.

03:56.190 --> 03:57.190
We received reports

03:57.190 --> 03:58.560
that you've harassed multiple women

03:58.560 --> 04:00.080
and are suspected of being involved in
several rape cases.

04:00.080 --> 04:00.810
Come with me!

04:00.870 --> 04:01.770
Stop there! Stop there!

04:01.770 --> 04:03.000
Cuff him! Behave! Put the cuffs on!

04:03.000 --> 04:03.750
Cuff him! Behave!

04:03.750 --> 04:04.870
You've got the wrong person!

04:04.870 --> 04:05.710
Move! Move!

04:11.860 --> 04:13.910
Running away won't solve the problem.

04:13.910 --> 04:15.150
The way to stop rumors

04:15.680 --> 04:16.630
is to face them

04:17.000 --> 04:18.730
and defeat them with the truth.

04:25.680 --> 04:27.190
The police came so quickly.

04:27.190 --> 04:29.590
You must have done a lot
these past few days.

04:29.920 --> 04:30.520
Thank you.

04:32.110 --> 04:32.909
It's nothing.

04:39.000 --> 04:39.510
How did you know

04:39.510 --> 04:40.770
he would be here today?

04:41.190 --> 04:43.159
I've asked around about this Zhang Erlai.

04:43.159 --> 04:44.630
He spends his days idly

04:44.630 --> 04:45.510
wandering around the village,

04:45.510 --> 04:46.770
and he's quite handsy.

04:47.159 --> 04:48.070
Many girls

04:48.159 --> 04:49.720
have been taken advantage of by him,

04:49.720 --> 04:51.120
but they don't dare speak up.

04:51.120 --> 04:52.450
Someone had to stand up.

04:53.240 --> 04:54.240
That's why I came.

04:56.000 --> 04:56.600
By the way,

04:56.920 --> 04:58.480
I need to thank you and Kang Wei.

04:58.480 --> 04:59.360
I know that these past few days,

04:59.360 --> 05:00.620
you've both done a lot.

05:01.800 --> 05:02.930
Even without us two,

05:03.360 --> 05:04.190
you've already thought of

05:04.190 --> 05:04.920
a solution,

05:05.310 --> 05:05.800
right?

05:06.360 --> 05:07.000
It seems like

05:07.000 --> 05:08.510
you don't need to rely on anyone.

05:08.510 --> 05:10.110
You can do so much on your own.

05:12.040 --> 05:13.510
I want to do even more.

05:14.920 --> 05:16.250
Now that I've come here,

05:16.270 --> 05:17.510
I want to live this life

05:17.510 --> 05:18.370
to the fullest.

05:20.830 --> 05:21.560
You're saying things

05:21.560 --> 05:23.020
I don't understand again.

05:23.750 --> 05:24.510
Ms. Xiaolan,

05:25.240 --> 05:26.770
you're really mysterious.

05:28.460 --> 05:29.660
Yes, I am mysterious.

05:29.950 --> 05:30.870
So don't think

05:30.870 --> 05:32.470
you can easily figure me out.

05:36.950 --> 05:39.480
Looks like I won't
make any money today again.

05:41.360 --> 05:42.510
If one day,

05:43.510 --> 05:45.110
you get to make a lot of money,

05:45.870 --> 05:46.800
what will you do?

05:48.430 --> 05:49.360
I'll buy a house,

05:49.720 --> 05:50.430
buy a car,

05:51.070 --> 05:52.670
and reach the peak of my life.

05:55.680 --> 05:57.560
The most important thing right now
is making money

05:57.560 --> 06:00.160
and paying back my living expenses
to my uncle.

06:00.900 --> 06:01.630
It seems like

06:02.240 --> 06:04.840
you have a good relationship
with your family.

06:06.190 --> 06:08.070
I'm merely returning their favor.

06:08.070 --> 06:10.120
It used to be my uncle's family of three

06:10.120 --> 06:11.270
living in that small courtyard.

06:11.270 --> 06:12.480
How comfortable they must have been
back then.

06:12.480 --> 06:13.910
Now with my mom and I staying with them,

06:13.910 --> 06:14.750
we're inevitably

06:14.750 --> 06:16.010
causing them trouble.

06:16.230 --> 06:17.270
Even with family,

06:18.240 --> 06:19.700
I don't want to owe anyone.

06:20.160 --> 06:23.690
So as for others, I definitely don't want
to be indebted to them.

06:25.360 --> 06:26.360
Comrade Xiaolan.

06:26.630 --> 06:27.760
Have you always been

06:27.950 --> 06:29.750
keeping people at arm's length?

06:30.240 --> 06:31.120
Or is it just me?

06:31.950 --> 06:34.150
Is there something I'm not doing right?

06:36.120 --> 06:37.390
Mr. Zhou.

06:38.600 --> 06:40.460
You haven't done anything wrong.

06:40.720 --> 06:41.600
It's just that

06:41.800 --> 06:42.870
you really don't fit

06:42.870 --> 06:44.159
into my life plans.

06:45.310 --> 06:46.159
As you can see,

06:46.630 --> 06:47.510
my living situation

06:47.510 --> 06:49.070
is already terrible enough.

06:49.070 --> 06:49.830
Just trying to improve it

06:49.830 --> 06:51.870
takes up so much of my time.

06:52.159 --> 06:55.560
I really don't have more energy
to think about anything else.

06:56.630 --> 06:57.560
I know we haven't known each other

06:57.560 --> 06:58.360
for very long,

06:58.870 --> 07:00.430
and we don't know much about each other.

07:00.430 --> 07:01.160
But I believe

07:01.800 --> 07:03.060
you're a brave person.

07:03.430 --> 07:04.160
I hope

07:04.510 --> 07:06.000
you won't close yourself off

07:06.000 --> 07:07.330
because of some rumors.

07:07.600 --> 07:09.400
You won't be stuck here forever.

07:09.750 --> 07:10.950
I'll also keep trying

07:11.190 --> 07:11.920
to earn

07:12.190 --> 07:13.160
a place in your

07:13.160 --> 07:14.090
life plans soon.

07:15.800 --> 07:16.800
Whatever you say.

07:18.680 --> 07:19.680
Comrade Xiaolan.

07:19.720 --> 07:20.720
Comrade Xiaolan!

07:21.630 --> 07:22.830
I came to see you today

07:22.870 --> 07:24.870
not just to resolve Zhang Erlai's matter,

07:24.870 --> 07:26.200
but also to say goodbye.

07:26.870 --> 07:28.720
I received a telegram from the capital.

07:28.720 --> 07:30.380
I've spent too much time here.

07:30.630 --> 07:31.630
I must go back now.

07:31.950 --> 07:32.480
However,

07:32.830 --> 07:34.159
whenever I get the chance,

07:34.159 --> 07:35.560
I'll come back to see you.

07:36.310 --> 07:37.120
You should focus on

07:37.120 --> 07:38.190
your own affairs.

07:40.560 --> 07:41.490
It's no trouble.

07:48.360 --> 07:49.420
Stop following me.

07:49.800 --> 07:50.600
I've arrived.

07:53.070 --> 07:53.670
Oh, right.

07:54.800 --> 07:56.040
This is a stun baton.

07:57.000 --> 07:58.870
It can protect you when necessary.

07:58.870 --> 08:00.400
Let me show you how to use it.

08:00.480 --> 08:00.920
Look,

08:01.240 --> 08:02.270
this is the safety.

08:02.270 --> 08:03.600
Press it once to unlock.

08:03.950 --> 08:05.430
And this is the switch.

08:05.830 --> 08:06.430
Like this.

08:12.660 --> 08:13.360
I didn't know they had

08:13.360 --> 08:15.620
such sophisticated gadgets these days.

08:16.230 --> 08:16.920
Stay safe.

08:17.270 --> 08:17.870
Thank you.

08:18.480 --> 08:19.140
No problem.

08:22.560 --> 08:24.310
This is my address.

08:25.040 --> 08:26.720
Can we be pen pals?

08:25.660 --> 08:26.960
[Send Friend Request]

08:39.909 --> 08:40.909
I'll be going now.

08:41.080 --> 08:42.080
Comrade Xiaolan.

08:42.179 --> 08:43.200
I wish you all the best.

08:43.200 --> 08:43.730
Goodbye.

08:44.350 --> 08:44.880
Bye-bye.

08:49.420 --> 08:50.180
Pen pals...

08:50.630 --> 08:51.960
Remember to write to me.

09:09.170 --> 09:10.500
Friend request withdrawn.

09:09.220 --> 09:10.990
[Friend Request]

09:10.850 --> 09:11.510
Never mind.

09:23.000 --> 09:23.460
This...

09:23.630 --> 09:24.390
Xiaolan, what did you just say

09:24.390 --> 09:25.660
this dish is called again?

09:25.660 --> 09:28.000
It's called duck egg version of mock crab.

09:29.000 --> 09:30.200
Mock crab?

09:30.360 --> 09:31.670
I've never had real crabs before,

09:31.670 --> 09:33.330
but this is really delicious.

09:33.390 --> 09:33.910
Really good.

09:33.910 --> 09:35.390
Our Xiaolan always makes these

09:35.390 --> 09:36.390
creative dishes.

09:37.550 --> 09:39.120
Next time when we sell duck eggs,

09:39.120 --> 09:40.750
make a plate of this for the customers
to try first.

09:40.750 --> 09:42.670
This way, the eggs will sell better.

09:42.670 --> 09:44.080
Letting them try for free?

09:44.080 --> 09:45.480
Isn't that too generous?

09:46.150 --> 09:46.750
No,

09:46.840 --> 09:48.900
this is called a marketing strategy.

09:49.240 --> 09:50.890
Don't worry, I'll calculate the costs.

09:50.890 --> 09:51.660
W-What strategy?

09:51.660 --> 09:52.480
What does that mean?

09:52.480 --> 09:54.120
Marketing strategy.

09:54.140 --> 09:55.540
Never heard of that term.

09:56.910 --> 09:57.440
Eat more.

09:59.480 --> 10:00.010
Xiaolan.

10:00.550 --> 10:02.750
Now that Zhang Erlai has been arrested,

10:02.870 --> 10:04.440
he won't come looking for you again,
will he?

10:04.440 --> 10:05.700
He won't. Don't worry.

10:06.220 --> 10:07.190
We're all keeping an eye on him.

10:07.190 --> 10:08.190
He wouldn't dare.

10:10.750 --> 10:11.280
Fengmei.

10:11.320 --> 10:12.600
New Year is coming soon.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.630
Hurry and buy some oil cakes.

10:13.630 --> 10:15.090
The pigs need to fatten up.

10:19.240 --> 10:19.900
Uncle Yong.

10:20.960 --> 10:21.420
Auntie.

10:21.630 --> 10:22.270
Chen Qing.

10:22.960 --> 10:23.930
Are you on holiday?

10:23.930 --> 10:24.190
Yes.

10:24.200 --> 10:25.000
Come in and have some food.

10:25.000 --> 10:26.000
No need, I've already eaten.

10:26.000 --> 10:27.750
I came to get Uncle Yong
to answer the phone.

10:27.750 --> 10:29.360
The village committee called.

10:29.360 --> 10:29.910
Who is it?

10:30.240 --> 10:32.770
They said they need you
for bricklaying work.

10:34.660 --> 10:35.750
Coming, coming.

10:35.780 --> 10:36.440
I'm coming.

10:56.160 --> 10:57.620
Auntie, I'll be going now.

10:57.800 --> 10:59.150
I'll close the door for you.

10:59.150 --> 10:59.790
Okay.

11:00.200 --> 11:01.200
Come visit again.

11:06.600 --> 11:07.200
Auntie.

11:07.570 --> 11:09.200
How long has Uncle been working

11:09.200 --> 11:10.130
as a bricklayer?

11:10.200 --> 11:11.530
For over half a year now.

11:12.200 --> 11:13.000
You know what,

11:13.320 --> 11:14.720
this job pays quite well.

11:14.910 --> 11:15.940
See, that tricycle

11:15.940 --> 11:17.150
you use to sell duck eggs,

11:17.150 --> 11:18.150
and this bicycle—

11:18.360 --> 11:19.360
all of these were bought by your uncle

11:19.360 --> 11:20.550
after he started working

11:20.550 --> 11:21.480
as a bricklayer.

11:23.720 --> 11:25.580
Is bricklaying that profitable?

11:42.360 --> 11:42.870
Here.

11:43.830 --> 11:45.560
It's cold at night. Put this on.

11:49.120 --> 11:49.780
Sit with me.

12:02.550 --> 12:03.150
Xiaolan,

12:04.960 --> 12:07.670
you put away that alarm clock?

12:11.240 --> 12:12.100
When it's dawn,

12:12.600 --> 12:14.000
the sunlight wakes me up.

12:14.440 --> 12:15.770
I don't need it anymore.

12:34.420 --> 12:35.010
Xiaolan.

12:42.120 --> 12:42.720
Xiaolan.

12:43.710 --> 12:44.600
Are you enjoying

12:44.600 --> 12:45.660
our trip this time?

12:46.240 --> 12:47.000
Yes.

12:48.030 --> 12:48.630
Then how about we

12:48.630 --> 12:50.550
come out every year? Would you like that?

12:50.550 --> 12:51.080
Yes.

12:51.720 --> 12:52.960
Where should we go next time,

12:52.960 --> 12:54.160
Xiaolan? You decide.

12:55.720 --> 12:57.120
I want to...

13:14.360 --> 13:20.660
[In Surgery]

13:30.360 --> 13:32.000
Miss, how are my parents?

13:32.030 --> 13:32.510
Xiaolan.

13:32.510 --> 13:32.910
I'm sorry.

13:32.910 --> 13:33.840
-You can't go in.
-I'm sorry.

13:33.840 --> 13:35.370
Let's wait a little longer.

13:36.030 --> 13:36.630
Xiaolan.

13:36.910 --> 13:39.030
Your parents are still being resuscitated
in there.

13:39.030 --> 13:39.760
Don't worry.

13:39.870 --> 13:40.670
It'll be okay.

13:40.910 --> 13:42.080
They'll be out soon.

13:48.030 --> 13:48.490
Doctor.

13:48.630 --> 13:49.150
Doctor.

13:49.630 --> 13:51.480
How are my sister and brother-in-law?

13:51.480 --> 13:52.410
I'm truly sorry.

13:52.510 --> 13:54.040
We did everything we could.

13:56.030 --> 13:57.390
I want my mom and dad!

13:57.440 --> 13:58.320
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

13:58.320 --> 13:59.220
I want my mom and dad!

13:59.220 --> 13:59.980
Xiaolan!

14:00.120 --> 14:02.360
I want my mom and dad!

14:03.320 --> 14:04.000
Xiaolan!

14:15.320 --> 14:16.440
Perhaps it's fate,

14:17.790 --> 14:19.850
or perhaps it's written in the stars.

14:21.670 --> 14:22.750
Although I've come to

14:22.750 --> 14:24.000
a strange place,

14:25.240 --> 14:26.120
I've gained

14:27.030 --> 14:28.440
a sense of family love

14:28.070 --> 14:33.440
♪ Watching the flowers fall, I, lonely,
ask the night sky ♪

14:28.630 --> 14:30.030
that I never had before.

14:31.550 --> 14:32.950
Since I can't leave here,

14:33.720 --> 14:34.720
I'll just make the best

14:34.440 --> 14:39.190
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

14:35.320 --> 14:37.750
of whatever time I have.

14:41.520 --> 14:45.940
♪ Time is upside down,
the seasons intertwine ♪

14:41.670 --> 14:42.270
Mom.

14:44.720 --> 14:46.120
When you were little,

14:47.160 --> 14:53.190
♪ Fate seems to want us to stay silent ♪

14:47.240 --> 14:49.370
you used to like to lean on my shoulder.

14:54.120 --> 14:54.600
Mom.

14:54.480 --> 15:00.190
♪ Time is so stingy,
even memories are hard to keep ♪

15:01.750 --> 15:02.840
I still like it now.

15:01.880 --> 15:08.740
♪ But I still remember
our promises of love ♪

15:07.670 --> 15:08.360
Alright.

15:09.490 --> 15:11.440
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

15:10.000 --> 15:11.330
Then keep leaning on me.

15:11.580 --> 15:15.850
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

15:16.280 --> 15:18.690
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

15:18.790 --> 15:19.720
Since I'm staying here,

15:18.840 --> 15:23.450
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

15:20.840 --> 15:22.640
I should live my life to the most.

15:23.800 --> 15:27.760
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

15:27.780 --> 15:31.840
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

15:32.660 --> 15:36.980
♪ Together, forever ♪

15:43.960 --> 15:44.490
Xiaolan.

15:45.750 --> 15:46.600
I've prepared some

15:46.600 --> 15:47.510
dumplings and eggs for you.

15:47.510 --> 15:49.040
-No need.
-Eat it on the way.

15:49.240 --> 15:49.570
Here.

15:50.200 --> 15:51.400
Be careful, alright?

15:53.630 --> 15:54.120
Okay.

15:54.440 --> 15:55.170
Thanks, Mom.

15:55.320 --> 15:55.790
I'm off.

15:56.840 --> 15:57.750
Be careful.

16:02.390 --> 16:02.910
Fen.

16:04.000 --> 16:04.870
Where did she go

16:04.870 --> 16:06.200
so early in the morning?

16:06.750 --> 16:08.950
Xiaolan said she wanted to try her luck.

16:09.000 --> 16:10.270
I wonder if business

16:10.270 --> 16:12.200
in the provincial capital is good.

16:14.120 --> 16:14.850
Don't worry.

16:26.060 --> 16:30.260
[Capital]

16:31.270 --> 16:31.720
Wei.

16:32.430 --> 16:33.030
Come here.

16:34.030 --> 16:34.630
What's up?

16:36.080 --> 16:38.200
Can you help me analyze something?

16:38.480 --> 16:39.280
About Anqing.

16:42.440 --> 16:44.360
You've come to the right person.

16:44.930 --> 16:45.320
Let me tell you.

16:45.320 --> 16:46.750
Although I'm a year younger than you,

16:46.750 --> 16:47.860
I started working earlier.

16:47.860 --> 16:49.120
When it comes to social experience,

16:49.120 --> 16:50.580
mine is richer than yours.

16:50.670 --> 16:51.240
Let me tell you.

16:51.240 --> 16:52.390
When pursuing a girl,

16:52.390 --> 16:53.630
you can't be too direct.

16:53.630 --> 16:55.760
You need to figure out her needs

16:55.790 --> 16:57.320
and then strike precisely.

16:58.790 --> 16:59.720
Her needs?

17:00.840 --> 17:02.100
What does she need now?

17:02.150 --> 17:02.840
Money?

17:03.960 --> 17:06.220
You'll have to figure that out yourself.

17:07.240 --> 17:08.960
When are we going to Anqing again?

17:08.960 --> 17:10.069
From what you're saying,

17:10.069 --> 17:11.069
it seems like we need to go there often.

17:11.069 --> 17:12.670
Think you're so clever, huh?

17:14.800 --> 17:18.410
[Shangdu]

17:41.440 --> 17:42.640
Even if I can't leave,

17:42.920 --> 17:44.030
at the very least,

17:44.310 --> 17:47.570
I should get myself to live in
a more familiar environment.

17:51.110 --> 17:52.910
If I want to make it into the city,

17:53.080 --> 17:54.610
going to college is one way,

18:00.720 --> 18:03.320
and getting rich by doing business
is another.

18:04.050 --> 18:05.770
With my current resources,

18:06.140 --> 18:07.400
[Agricultural products]

18:06.400 --> 18:08.790
trading agricultural products
would be the most convenient.

18:08.790 --> 18:10.400
But I'm not a real farmer,

18:10.960 --> 18:12.560
so I have no advantage there.

18:14.270 --> 18:16.160
In terms of profit margins,

18:16.230 --> 18:18.260
[Electronics]

18:16.460 --> 18:18.350
the electronics business
is most profitable.

18:18.350 --> 18:21.210
But the costs are too high,
and quotas are required.

18:21.400 --> 18:22.750
I don't stand a chance.

18:28.400 --> 18:31.270
Come check it out!
New clothes from Longcheng!

18:32.430 --> 18:34.400
Come take a look! New fashion!

18:34.680 --> 18:35.480
Longcheng?

18:36.710 --> 18:37.430
Clothing?

18:37.040 --> 18:38.720
[Clothing]

18:38.200 --> 18:39.270
This I know well.

18:39.750 --> 18:42.110
As long as I can save enough money
for inventory.

18:42.110 --> 18:42.590
Miss,

18:42.750 --> 18:43.880
come in and check out our clothes.

18:43.880 --> 18:45.340
They're all in new styles.

18:55.920 --> 18:57.550
The cost of one trip to Longcheng

18:57.550 --> 18:58.950
would be at least 40 or 50,

18:59.160 --> 19:00.920
plus it takes a week round trip.

19:01.480 --> 19:03.200
If I stock less than 600 worth

19:03.270 --> 19:04.410
and make less than 200 profit,

19:04.020 --> 19:05.730
[Travel Fee: 50 yuan, Duration: 7 days,
Cost: 600 yuan, Profit: 200 yuan]

19:04.830 --> 19:06.290
then it's not worth doing.

19:07.240 --> 19:09.500
After selling duck eggs for so many days,

19:09.640 --> 19:11.300
I've only saved less than 100.

19:12.790 --> 19:14.000
Where can I get

19:14.000 --> 19:14.930
600 for capital?

19:15.680 --> 19:16.750
See, that tricycle

19:16.750 --> 19:17.920
you use to sell duck eggs,

19:17.920 --> 19:18.920
and this bicycle—

19:19.040 --> 19:20.070
all of these were bought by your uncle

19:20.070 --> 19:21.470
after he started working

19:21.550 --> 19:22.480
as a bricklayer.

19:23.690 --> 19:25.770
Is bricklaying that profitable?

19:28.550 --> 19:30.810
Something's not right about this uncle.

19:38.400 --> 19:39.920
Auntie, what are oil cakes?

19:38.890 --> 19:40.040
[Shangdu Oil Refinery]

19:40.590 --> 19:42.030
They're the waste material

19:42.030 --> 19:43.310
left after pressing rapeseed oil.

19:43.310 --> 19:44.480
Pigs love to eat them,

19:44.480 --> 19:46.540
so every household needs to buy some.

19:47.160 --> 19:48.590
My thinking was too rigid.

19:48.590 --> 19:50.830
I only thought about
selling things to the city,

19:50.830 --> 19:52.560
never considered the reverse.

19:53.740 --> 19:55.110
Sir, turn left up ahead.

19:55.110 --> 19:55.720
Okay.

20:07.590 --> 20:08.440
Tao!

20:08.920 --> 20:09.750
Coming!

20:13.880 --> 20:15.480
Come on, let's carry these inside.

20:15.480 --> 20:16.210
What's this?

20:17.110 --> 20:18.470
So many oil cakes?

20:18.830 --> 20:20.000
I happened to pass by the oil mill

20:20.000 --> 20:21.160
and remembered about them.

20:21.160 --> 20:21.880
The tractor was heading this way,

20:21.880 --> 20:23.540
so I had them bring these back.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.000
But we won't need

20:26.000 --> 20:27.240
so many oil cakes.

20:28.310 --> 20:29.000
I know.

20:29.240 --> 20:31.640
Are you planning to
resell these oil cakes?

20:32.590 --> 20:33.390
Well, you see,

20:33.700 --> 20:35.200
isn't the competition of selling things

20:35.200 --> 20:36.550
from the village to the city fierce?

20:36.550 --> 20:38.080
Then we'll do the opposite—

20:39.080 --> 20:41.480
bringing city goods to sell
in the village.

20:41.790 --> 20:42.680
And then,

20:43.110 --> 20:44.550
I can use that tricycle

20:44.960 --> 20:47.070
to transport 100-200 catties at once.

20:47.070 --> 20:48.920
That's an advantage others don't have.

20:48.920 --> 20:50.920
I've realized you're truly

20:50.920 --> 20:52.450
a natural businessperson.

20:52.590 --> 20:53.480
These oil cakes

20:53.720 --> 20:56.180
are in short supply
for anyone raising pigs.

20:56.310 --> 20:58.100
It's troublesome to get them elsewhere,

20:58.100 --> 20:59.500
but you've brought so many back.

20:59.500 --> 21:01.500
Everyone will be fighting for them.

21:04.070 --> 21:04.680
Auntie.

21:05.030 --> 21:06.750
Let's keep some for ourselves.

21:06.750 --> 21:07.720
Didn't Uncle say

21:07.960 --> 21:09.550
we need to fatten up the pigs?

21:09.550 --> 21:10.080
Xiaolan,

21:10.200 --> 21:11.440
you're so thoughtful.

21:11.440 --> 21:11.920
Let's carry them back.

21:11.920 --> 21:12.310
Let me.

21:12.310 --> 21:13.070
Let me do it.

21:13.480 --> 21:14.610
I'll go get the cart.

21:24.720 --> 21:25.400
Xiaolan.

21:25.960 --> 21:26.440
Here.

21:27.550 --> 21:28.410
Soak your feet.

21:29.310 --> 21:30.510
It'll help you relax.

21:31.830 --> 21:32.590
You brought so many

21:32.590 --> 21:34.120
oil cakes back by yourself.

21:34.680 --> 21:35.100
Mom.

21:35.590 --> 21:36.920
Keep this money for now.

21:37.510 --> 21:38.440
We're lucky

21:38.510 --> 21:39.350
that Uncle

21:39.350 --> 21:40.440
lent us his tricycle,

21:40.440 --> 21:42.240
so we could sell these oil cakes.

21:42.300 --> 21:44.200
I can transport 300 catties in one trip

21:44.200 --> 21:45.660
and make 15 yuan each time.

21:46.200 --> 21:47.330
This way, in a month,

21:47.640 --> 21:49.510
I can complete
the initial capital accumulation.

21:49.510 --> 21:50.480
We won't have to do

21:50.480 --> 21:51.810
such hard work anymore.

21:51.910 --> 21:52.830
We can switch to businesses

21:52.830 --> 21:53.960
with higher profits

21:53.960 --> 21:56.090
and implement industrial upgrading.

21:57.270 --> 21:59.800
I don't understand
these terms you're using.

22:00.140 --> 22:01.340
All you need to know is

22:01.710 --> 22:03.430
that we'll have a better life.

22:05.240 --> 22:06.170
I believe in you.

22:08.110 --> 22:08.880
The two of us

22:09.510 --> 22:11.200
will surely be able to live

22:12.030 --> 22:13.790
a stable life like before.

22:14.680 --> 22:15.590
Like before?

22:16.720 --> 22:17.270
Mom,

22:17.590 --> 22:19.790
do you still want to go back
to the Xia family?

22:19.790 --> 22:20.400
You think

22:20.400 --> 22:21.270
that life from before

22:21.270 --> 22:22.480
was stable?

22:23.590 --> 22:25.320
We need to look forward in life,

22:25.680 --> 22:26.480
not backward.

22:26.920 --> 22:27.480
Well,

22:28.000 --> 22:28.720
Xiaolan.

22:30.510 --> 22:32.270
I know you're still upset.

22:33.600 --> 22:36.730
I didn't say anything about
going back to the Xia family.

22:38.310 --> 22:38.840
Alright.

22:39.350 --> 22:40.880
You keep this money for now.

22:41.030 --> 22:41.550
Come on,

22:41.880 --> 22:44.210
soak your feet before the water gets cold.

23:05.030 --> 23:05.510
Yong.

23:07.590 --> 23:08.790
Rest early, alright?

23:08.920 --> 23:10.780
Xiaolan must also be tired today.

23:12.030 --> 23:12.400
Yong.

23:13.400 --> 23:14.480
Don't you think Xiaolan

23:14.480 --> 23:15.400
has changed

23:16.550 --> 23:17.840
since her head injury?

23:18.370 --> 23:19.400
She keeps saying things

23:19.400 --> 23:20.530
I don't understand.

23:20.880 --> 23:21.550
Like industry

23:21.550 --> 23:23.030
and something called accu...

23:23.030 --> 23:24.360
Accumulation and such.

23:25.310 --> 23:26.440
This can't be right.

23:27.480 --> 23:28.720
Should I take her to the clinic tomorrow

23:28.720 --> 23:29.510
and get her checked?

23:29.510 --> 23:30.790
What's there to check?

23:31.440 --> 23:32.850
You're worrying for nothing.

23:32.850 --> 23:33.880
That kid is now walking

23:33.880 --> 23:35.270
on the right path.

23:35.520 --> 23:36.270
And even if

23:36.270 --> 23:37.660
you think her mind isn't working well,

23:37.660 --> 23:39.250
she's still moving
in a positive direction.

23:39.250 --> 23:40.970
You're just overthinking it.

23:41.440 --> 23:42.030
Really?

23:42.160 --> 23:43.290
Everything's fine.

23:44.310 --> 23:45.830
Should we tell Dajun

23:46.920 --> 23:48.440
about her business venture?

23:48.440 --> 23:49.700
Why tell him anything?

23:49.790 --> 23:51.640
That bastard doesn't deserve to know!

23:51.640 --> 23:52.750
Something this serious had happened,

23:52.750 --> 23:53.880
but did he ever care?

23:53.920 --> 23:56.000
He doesn't even deserve to
be Xiaolan's father!

23:56.000 --> 23:57.220
You're doing fine staying here with me.

23:57.220 --> 23:59.240
Why keep thinking about the Xia family?

23:59.240 --> 24:01.240
But I can't stay here forever.

24:01.830 --> 24:02.400
Yong.

24:02.680 --> 24:05.240
A woman should follow her husband,
for better or worse.

24:05.240 --> 24:07.040
I can't just never go back, can I?

24:07.480 --> 24:08.400
Why not?

24:09.720 --> 24:11.310
It's a new era now.

24:11.680 --> 24:13.160
Not only is marriage a choice,

24:13.160 --> 24:14.270
divorce is too.

24:17.050 --> 24:18.510
Heard what the kid said?

24:19.400 --> 24:20.240
Think about it. You two,

24:20.240 --> 24:21.160
back in the Xia family,

24:21.160 --> 24:22.400
almost lost your lives.

24:22.400 --> 24:23.260
The kid has finally

24:23.260 --> 24:24.460
gotten her life back,

24:24.510 --> 24:26.000
and she wants a better life now.

24:26.000 --> 24:27.600
Don't you dare hold her back.

24:34.880 --> 24:35.790
Hurry up!

24:36.070 --> 24:37.130
It's about to rain.

24:38.400 --> 24:39.440
If this grain gets wet,

24:39.440 --> 24:41.030
our whole year's work will be wasted!

24:41.030 --> 24:41.750
Hurry up!

24:42.160 --> 24:42.680
Come on!

24:47.480 --> 24:48.400
Hurry up!

24:50.360 --> 24:51.520
Quick, quick!

24:51.550 --> 24:53.160
This weather is really working against us.

24:53.160 --> 24:54.110
What's happening?

24:54.110 --> 24:55.590
It's about to rain! Collect the grain!

24:55.590 --> 24:56.440
It's about to rain!

24:56.440 --> 24:57.500
Collect the grain!

25:00.160 --> 25:01.000
Hurry! Hurry!

25:06.270 --> 25:07.200
Quick, get that!

25:07.240 --> 25:07.680
Here.

25:08.200 --> 25:09.130
Use this basket.

25:09.350 --> 25:10.310
Tao, be careful!

25:11.400 --> 25:12.400
Come on, let's go!

25:13.030 --> 25:13.680
Let's go!

25:14.240 --> 25:14.770
Careful.

25:16.790 --> 25:17.320
Let's go.

25:17.640 --> 25:18.100
Come on.

25:18.640 --> 25:19.030
Here.

25:23.160 --> 25:24.490
Put more effort into it!

25:25.750 --> 25:26.210
Come on.

25:32.070 --> 25:32.800
Give it to me.

25:37.110 --> 25:37.830
Come on.

25:38.110 --> 25:38.640
Let's go.

25:38.880 --> 25:39.550
Come on, let's go.

25:39.550 --> 25:40.200
Duck down.

25:40.400 --> 25:40.930
Let's go.

25:41.640 --> 25:42.510
Let's go.

25:44.200 --> 25:44.790
Hurry up.

25:45.160 --> 25:46.220
Let's go. Let's go.

25:54.920 --> 25:56.580
Come on, put your back into it.

25:56.680 --> 25:57.140
Come on!

25:57.240 --> 25:57.770
Hurry up!

25:58.550 --> 25:59.350
Hurry, hurry!

25:59.640 --> 26:00.400
Quick, quick!

26:00.400 --> 26:01.240
Careful. Careful.

26:01.240 --> 26:01.750
Hurry!

26:02.550 --> 26:03.350
This rain.

26:04.590 --> 26:05.590
Look at this rain,

26:05.920 --> 26:07.180
it's chasing after us!

26:09.240 --> 26:10.700
Thanks to Fen and Xiaolan.

26:11.160 --> 26:11.750
Otherwise, we

26:11.750 --> 26:13.080
couldn't have managed.

26:15.070 --> 26:16.110
Come on. Have some water.

26:16.110 --> 26:17.040
Have some water.

26:17.220 --> 26:18.080
I'm so thirsty.

26:21.200 --> 26:22.330
My son is so capable.

26:22.510 --> 26:23.660
You can even help with the chores now.

26:23.660 --> 26:25.530
Get a towel. Look how wet it is.

26:28.270 --> 26:29.530
Look at all this sweat.

26:29.790 --> 26:31.160
Even I feel like

26:31.550 --> 26:33.350
I look like part of their family.

26:34.510 --> 26:35.000
It seems

26:35.000 --> 26:36.550
I've already adapted to this place

26:36.550 --> 26:37.810
and adapted to the life

26:38.240 --> 26:40.100
of becoming another Xia Xiaolan.

26:41.070 --> 26:41.640
Xiaolan.

26:42.350 --> 26:43.200
Have some water. Here.

26:43.200 --> 26:44.270
I worked hard today.

26:44.270 --> 26:44.590
Good.

26:44.590 --> 26:45.400
What tasty food

26:45.400 --> 26:46.510
can I have for dinner?

26:46.510 --> 26:47.480
I'll fry you a sunny-side-up egg.

26:47.480 --> 26:48.140
How's that?

26:49.310 --> 26:51.400
One for you

26:51.480 --> 26:52.610
and one for Xiaolan.

27:06.790 --> 27:08.200
After so many days of drought,

27:08.200 --> 27:09.600
we finally got some rain.

27:09.680 --> 27:10.740
That's wonderful.

27:11.310 --> 27:12.240
This family

27:12.750 --> 27:14.810
is always making a fuss over nothing.

27:15.200 --> 27:16.680
Always in chaos.

27:17.590 --> 27:19.680
Always in a flurry.

27:20.830 --> 27:21.360
Xiaolan,

27:21.640 --> 27:23.170
what do you want for dinner?

27:26.070 --> 27:27.070
Anything's fine.

27:30.030 --> 27:31.010
I'll make her hand-pulled noodles.

27:31.010 --> 27:33.270
She loves hand-pulled noodles the most.

27:35.550 --> 27:36.590
And there's some

27:37.790 --> 27:39.650
warmth that I don't want to admit.

27:43.270 --> 27:45.550
Oh heavens!

27:46.240 --> 27:47.070
Hurry!

27:47.270 --> 27:48.070
Quick!

27:48.400 --> 27:48.960
Hurry up!

27:50.200 --> 27:51.480
Put it down!

27:52.400 --> 27:54.400
This year's harvest!

27:55.120 --> 27:56.080
Hurry up!

27:56.160 --> 27:57.510
Go quickly!

27:58.790 --> 28:00.850
Don't worry about that!

28:00.880 --> 28:02.030
Go now!

28:03.110 --> 28:03.550
You...

28:04.240 --> 28:06.170
Heavens, please stop raining!

28:06.200 --> 28:08.400
Oh heavens, please stop!

28:08.480 --> 28:09.350
Stop raining!

28:09.400 --> 28:11.240
Please stop! My grain!

28:12.030 --> 28:12.880
Dajun!

28:13.480 --> 28:14.590
Dajun, hurry!

28:14.720 --> 28:16.030
Go collect the grain!

28:16.030 --> 28:16.270
Okay!

28:16.270 --> 28:18.160
The grain is all soaked!

28:18.240 --> 28:18.510
Alright.

28:18.510 --> 28:19.160
Hurry up!

28:19.200 --> 28:19.590
Got it.

28:19.590 --> 28:20.550
Hurry!

28:22.160 --> 28:23.510
Good heavens.

28:23.510 --> 28:24.590
Let us collect

28:24.590 --> 28:25.680
all the grain back, please!

28:25.680 --> 28:26.790
Good heavens.

28:28.240 --> 28:29.680
My poor grain.

28:30.070 --> 28:30.830
Have some hot water.

28:30.830 --> 28:32.240
Soaked by the rain like this.

28:32.240 --> 28:33.590
Give me a drink quickly.
I'm dying of thirst.

28:33.590 --> 28:34.650
Alright, alright.

28:34.680 --> 28:35.810
Have some hot water.

28:36.160 --> 28:37.000
Alright.

28:37.160 --> 28:38.700
Seeing the millet soaked like this

28:38.700 --> 28:39.700
makes me so angry.

28:40.270 --> 28:42.070
We're so busy in this household,

28:42.090 --> 28:43.400
yet those two ran off
to her parents' home.

28:43.400 --> 28:45.270
They didn't even come back to check on us.

28:45.270 --> 28:47.470
As if they're not part of the Xia family.

28:48.550 --> 28:49.410
I'm so thirsty.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.000
Dajun,

28:50.830 --> 28:52.240
tell me the truth today.

28:52.920 --> 28:55.580
Are you going to continue that marriage
or what?

28:56.000 --> 28:57.680
Those two, Liu Fen and her daughter,

28:57.680 --> 28:59.030
they really know how to avoid work.

28:59.030 --> 29:01.030
We're so busy on the farms right now,

29:01.420 --> 29:02.790
yet they've run off to her mother's home.

29:02.790 --> 29:03.990
Mother, look at that.

29:06.960 --> 29:08.360
I'll bring them two back.

29:12.790 --> 29:14.350
A few days ago,

29:14.350 --> 29:16.010
I ran into Xia Xiaolan in town.

29:16.200 --> 29:17.640
She seemed to be selling duck eggs.

29:17.640 --> 29:19.550
And there was a man standing beside her.

29:19.550 --> 29:21.610
-Really?
-And he was quite handsome.

29:22.480 --> 29:23.010
Hongxia.

29:23.720 --> 29:24.590
Take Junshan and Junbao inside.

29:24.590 --> 29:26.270
What are you grinning about? Go inside.

29:26.270 --> 29:27.440
Go play inside. Go.

29:29.590 --> 29:30.190
This room.

29:31.510 --> 29:31.970
Mother.

29:32.470 --> 29:34.240
Hongxia is a very honest kid.

29:34.350 --> 29:35.380
She never lies.

29:35.720 --> 29:37.160
Who knows

29:37.400 --> 29:39.110
what Xiaolan was actually doing there?

29:39.110 --> 29:40.830
Luckily, it was Hongxia who saw her.

29:40.830 --> 29:42.430
If it had been an outsider...

29:45.920 --> 29:46.320
Right?

29:46.680 --> 29:47.740
Alright, alright.

29:47.790 --> 29:48.830
It's normal for family members

29:48.830 --> 29:50.030
to have disagreements.

29:50.030 --> 29:51.070
Let's have Xiaolan come back first

29:51.070 --> 29:52.550
and apologize to her grandmother.

29:52.550 --> 29:54.150
Then we can still be a family.

29:54.560 --> 29:55.690
She acted

29:55.720 --> 29:56.960
without thinking of the consequences.

29:56.960 --> 29:58.960
Look how upset she made her grandma.

29:59.510 --> 30:02.240
It's okay that I got upset.

30:02.750 --> 30:03.820
The main thing is that Ziyu

30:03.820 --> 30:05.060
has been wronged.

30:06.030 --> 30:06.920
Ziyu is

30:06.920 --> 30:08.000
being the bigger person.

30:08.000 --> 30:09.400
That's because she's generous,

30:09.400 --> 30:10.030
right?

30:11.790 --> 30:13.850
Tomorrow, I'll go to Qijing Village,

30:13.880 --> 30:15.030
bring them back,

30:16.270 --> 30:18.110
and have Xiaolan write an apology letter
to Ziyu.

30:18.110 --> 30:19.590
If one isn't enough, then two.

30:19.590 --> 30:20.110
Until

30:20.640 --> 30:21.770
Ziyu forgives them.

30:24.310 --> 30:25.440
That's more like it.

30:27.510 --> 30:28.070
Mother.

30:28.920 --> 30:29.780
How about this?

30:30.040 --> 30:30.550
Tomorrow,

30:30.550 --> 30:31.880
I'll go with Dajun.

30:32.430 --> 30:34.440
Men can be a bit too blunt when they talk.

30:34.440 --> 30:36.040
Let's not make things worse.

30:37.590 --> 30:38.120
Alright.

30:38.510 --> 30:38.970
Mother.

30:39.160 --> 30:40.030
Then it's settled.

30:40.030 --> 30:41.270
I'll go with them.

30:41.550 --> 30:43.480
This time, we'll bring Fen back

30:43.550 --> 30:45.200
even if we have to carry her on the back.

30:45.200 --> 30:45.730
Alright.

30:46.110 --> 30:46.640
Alright.

30:48.080 --> 30:48.790
She just won't leave me alone.

30:48.790 --> 30:49.610
Now we just need

30:49.610 --> 30:51.800
to hope for the rain to stop

30:51.830 --> 30:53.290
and for the sun to come out.

30:58.400 --> 30:59.720
Can you count it properly?

30:59.720 --> 31:00.920
If not, just go to bed.

31:01.270 --> 31:02.350
What do you know?

31:02.920 --> 31:04.960
I'm arranging the money neatly.

31:05.510 --> 31:06.660
Only when you treat money well

31:06.660 --> 31:08.120
will money treat you well.

31:08.720 --> 31:10.270
Alright, tomorrow,

31:10.960 --> 31:12.790
bring Xia Xiaolan back.

31:13.110 --> 31:14.000
Ziyu is right.

31:14.790 --> 31:17.790
We'll only feel at ease
when she's right in front of us.

31:18.030 --> 31:18.830
Get on with it.

31:22.590 --> 31:23.400
Don't sleep yet.

31:23.400 --> 31:24.200
Listen.

31:24.590 --> 31:25.400
What if I get her

31:25.400 --> 31:26.310
a husband?

31:26.880 --> 31:27.740
Think about it.

31:28.030 --> 31:29.750
Once she's married off,

31:29.920 --> 31:31.180
it's settled for life.

31:31.680 --> 31:34.680
She won't be able to
ruin our daughter's life anymore.

31:34.720 --> 31:35.680
Have you lost your mind?

31:35.680 --> 31:36.720
With her reputation,

31:36.720 --> 31:37.850
who would marry her?

31:38.000 --> 31:38.790
Finding a husband?

31:38.790 --> 31:39.640
If she could find a widower

31:39.640 --> 31:40.400
or an old bachelor,

31:40.400 --> 31:41.510
that would be a blessing already.

31:41.510 --> 31:42.440
You understand?

31:42.880 --> 31:45.540
And you're talking about finding her
a husband.

31:46.200 --> 31:46.750
Right.

31:47.180 --> 31:48.270
I just thought of someone.

31:48.270 --> 31:49.400
You startled me.

31:49.640 --> 31:50.270
Who?

31:50.920 --> 31:51.650
Zhang Erlai.

31:53.760 --> 31:54.760
Right!

31:54.790 --> 31:56.750
If she gets together with Zhang Erlai,

31:56.750 --> 31:58.200
we'll even get some bride price.

31:58.200 --> 31:59.590
We can use it to support our Ziyu.

31:59.590 --> 32:01.110
She'll need a lot of money in the capital,

32:01.110 --> 32:01.590
right?

32:02.480 --> 32:04.270
I didn't think of that.

32:05.590 --> 32:07.200
You're so clever.

32:07.600 --> 32:09.200
If she gets together with Zhang Erlai,

32:09.200 --> 32:11.060
we'll have some bride price to...

32:12.400 --> 32:13.730
Wait, that's not right.

32:13.960 --> 32:14.720
What now?

32:15.240 --> 32:17.030
If she gets together with Zhang Erlai

32:17.030 --> 32:18.510
and the note incident gets revealed,

32:18.510 --> 32:19.110
what then?

32:19.440 --> 32:20.830
So what if it does?

32:21.440 --> 32:22.770
What can she do about it?

32:22.890 --> 32:23.690
By that time,

32:23.720 --> 32:24.830
even if she knows, what can she do?

32:24.830 --> 32:25.440
Tell me.

32:26.550 --> 32:29.410
Thinking about useless things all day.
Go to sleep.

32:30.160 --> 32:30.960
That's right.

32:31.240 --> 32:32.640
What can she possibly do?

32:34.030 --> 32:35.290
She can't do anything.

32:35.830 --> 32:36.720
First thing tomorrow morning,

32:36.720 --> 32:38.030
I'll go get her.

32:38.830 --> 32:41.360
Bringing her back early
will save us trouble.

33:09.270 --> 33:10.870
I really can't walk anymore.

33:11.200 --> 33:13.550
Can't you two slow down?

33:14.390 --> 33:16.110
Hurry up, Sister-in-law.

33:16.110 --> 33:18.000
We still need to get back today.

33:18.160 --> 33:20.160
This village is all mountain paths.

33:20.360 --> 33:21.960
I really can't walk anymore.

33:38.680 --> 33:40.010
Isn't that Xia Xiaolan?

33:40.030 --> 33:40.960
How can you not greet your elders

33:40.960 --> 33:41.960
-when you meet them?
-Xiaolan?

33:41.960 --> 33:42.890
It really is her.

33:44.440 --> 33:45.070
Xiaolan.

33:45.550 --> 33:46.790
We've come to get you.

33:47.610 --> 33:49.850
Seeing your father and aunts,

33:49.880 --> 33:51.540
how can you not even say hello?

33:53.000 --> 33:53.590
It seems

33:54.230 --> 33:55.890
this is Xia Xiaolan's father,

33:56.090 --> 33:57.000
Xia Dajun.

33:59.400 --> 34:00.480
Xia Dajun, right?

34:03.240 --> 34:04.970
She's calling you by your name.

34:05.690 --> 34:08.020
What are you doing here in Qijing Village?

34:08.760 --> 34:09.630
You... How dare you talk to

34:09.630 --> 34:10.550
me like that?

34:11.820 --> 34:12.510
If it weren't for

34:12.510 --> 34:13.510
my mother's sake,

34:13.590 --> 34:14.620
I wouldn't even bother with you.

34:14.620 --> 34:15.230
This kid...

34:15.230 --> 34:16.230
Stop right there!

34:18.760 --> 34:20.219
Let me tell you something.

34:21.000 --> 34:21.929
Don't start a fight.

34:21.929 --> 34:23.110
-Talk properly.
-Yeah.

34:23.110 --> 34:24.440
So many people are watching.

34:24.440 --> 34:25.320
Whatever issues we have,

34:25.320 --> 34:26.360
we can talk back at home.

34:26.360 --> 34:27.040
Let's talk properly.

34:27.040 --> 34:28.040
Tell your mother

34:28.060 --> 34:29.710
to pack up and come home with me.

34:29.710 --> 34:31.170
I'm here to bring you back.

34:31.520 --> 34:33.070
Your grandmother has forgiven you.

34:33.070 --> 34:33.870
That's right.

34:34.280 --> 34:35.000
Did you come all this way

34:35.000 --> 34:35.880
to tell jokes?

34:36.360 --> 34:38.030
What do you mean she forgave me?

34:38.030 --> 34:39.560
I haven't forgiven her yet.

34:39.760 --> 34:40.889
Didn't she tell you?

34:40.920 --> 34:42.550
I will never go back to the Xia family.

34:42.550 --> 34:44.190
I won't let my mother go back either

34:44.190 --> 34:45.639
to continue being your slaves.

34:45.639 --> 34:46.400
Hey, this kid...

34:46.400 --> 34:47.199
Hey, Xiaolan.

34:47.440 --> 34:48.510
How dare you speak like that?

34:48.510 --> 34:49.030
You're just a youngster,

34:49.030 --> 34:50.000
and we three elders

34:50.000 --> 34:51.230
can't even persuade you?

34:51.230 --> 34:51.760
Xiaolan.

34:52.110 --> 34:53.190
Listen to me.

34:53.590 --> 34:54.230
Come back home

34:54.230 --> 34:56.280
and apologize properly
to your grandmother.

34:56.280 --> 34:57.680
Then talk things through

34:57.880 --> 34:58.800
with your sister Ziyu.

34:58.800 --> 34:59.400
Ziyu

34:59.400 --> 35:00.230
will surely forgive you.

35:00.230 --> 35:01.030
That's right.

35:01.360 --> 35:02.760
We're all family.

35:04.440 --> 35:05.550
Who's your family?

35:05.760 --> 35:06.820
Let me say it again.

35:07.360 --> 35:08.670
I will absolutely never

35:08.670 --> 35:09.760
return to the Xia family.

35:09.760 --> 35:11.760
I won't let my mother go back either.

35:12.150 --> 35:13.400
The stigma between me and Zhang Erlai

35:13.400 --> 35:15.190
has been cleared by my own efforts.

35:15.190 --> 35:16.880
Zhang Erlai has been arrested.

35:16.880 --> 35:18.550
As for what happened with that note,

35:18.550 --> 35:20.610
I believe the police will resolve it.

35:20.630 --> 35:21.590
Tell Xia Ziyu

35:22.150 --> 35:23.440
that although I haven't caught her

35:23.440 --> 35:25.070
with evidence of her false accusations,

35:25.070 --> 35:26.480
I will never let her off.

35:29.630 --> 35:30.630
Zhang Erlai was arrested?

35:30.630 --> 35:32.690
I don't know. Haven't heard about it.

35:33.710 --> 35:35.550
This has nothing to do with our Ziyu...

35:35.550 --> 35:36.840
Even if all men in the world

35:36.840 --> 35:37.800
were to die...

35:38.000 --> 35:38.800
Don't point your finger at me.

35:38.800 --> 35:39.710
I would absolutely never

35:39.710 --> 35:40.970
seduce Xia Ziyu's man.

35:41.800 --> 35:43.030
You all know the truth

35:43.400 --> 35:45.230
about what was going on between them.

35:45.230 --> 35:46.960
Don't try to put the blame on me.

35:48.230 --> 35:49.000
And you,

35:49.920 --> 35:51.000
Xia Dajun, right?

35:52.000 --> 35:53.070
As my father,

35:53.760 --> 35:54.800
you never once tried

35:54.800 --> 35:56.860
to understand what really happened.

35:57.110 --> 35:57.960
When rumors were

35:57.960 --> 35:59.490
driving me to desperation,

35:59.550 --> 36:01.810
did you feel even
a bit of sympathy for me?

36:01.840 --> 36:02.970
After all this time,

36:03.080 --> 36:04.210
did you ever think of

36:04.230 --> 36:06.030
confronting Zhang Erlai
and settling the score with him?

36:06.030 --> 36:07.630
No, you didn't, right?

36:08.110 --> 36:08.760
So tell me,

36:09.230 --> 36:10.880
why should I go back to the Xia family?

36:10.880 --> 36:12.250
Why should I go back to being treated
like a slave

36:12.250 --> 36:14.180
when I could live my life decently?

36:15.670 --> 36:17.440
Don't get physical. Stop it.

36:17.480 --> 36:17.960
Don't get physical.

36:17.960 --> 36:18.630
Let's talk this through.

36:18.630 --> 36:19.480
How could you speak

36:19.480 --> 36:20.000
to your father like that?

36:20.000 --> 36:20.760
Xiaolan. Xiaolan.

36:20.760 --> 36:21.590
You've gone too far.

36:21.590 --> 36:22.360
We came here today

36:22.360 --> 36:23.190
for another reason.

36:23.190 --> 36:24.160
We need to see Liu Fen.

36:24.160 --> 36:25.190
Let's go. Take us to Liu Fen.

36:25.190 --> 36:25.710
Let's go.

36:25.710 --> 36:26.770
You must be joking.

36:27.030 --> 36:28.150
You think I'll do whatever you say?

36:28.150 --> 36:29.110
What's wrong with you?

36:29.110 --> 36:30.440
Where are your manners?

36:30.550 --> 36:31.420
No respect for your elders at all.

36:31.420 --> 36:32.680
Xia Dajun, look at this!

36:32.680 --> 36:34.010
Have you lost your mind?

36:34.120 --> 36:35.230
We are all your elders.

36:35.230 --> 36:37.070
How dare you speak to us like that?

36:37.070 --> 36:37.920
Elders?

36:39.550 --> 36:41.030
The elders

36:41.030 --> 36:41.850
who wish me dead?

36:41.850 --> 36:43.180
Hey, this kid is just...

36:43.190 --> 36:44.590
She's speaking with absolutely no respect

36:44.590 --> 36:45.670
and no sense of propriety at all now.

36:45.670 --> 36:46.670
If she were Ziyu,

36:46.670 --> 36:47.920
I would have beaten her already,
I'm telling you.

36:47.920 --> 36:49.480
Today, in front of everyone,

36:49.480 --> 36:50.960
I'll make it clear to everyone

36:50.960 --> 36:51.980
who your father is!

36:51.980 --> 36:53.240
You ungrateful child!

36:53.670 --> 36:55.230
You dare to hit your own father?

36:55.230 --> 36:55.910
Stop fighting!

36:55.910 --> 36:57.570
I'll teach you a lesson today!

37:00.510 --> 37:01.170
Uncle Yong!

37:01.670 --> 37:02.330
Uncle Yong!

37:03.710 --> 37:04.440
The Xia family...

37:04.440 --> 37:05.480
Some people from the Xia family are here.

37:05.480 --> 37:06.590
They're having a fight with Xiaolan.

37:06.590 --> 37:07.110
What?

37:07.400 --> 37:08.000
I'll go check.

37:08.000 --> 37:08.540
No, don't!

37:08.540 --> 37:09.540
Fen, listen to me.

37:09.550 --> 37:10.480
Stay in the yard.

37:10.710 --> 37:11.110
Qing,

37:11.150 --> 37:12.360
keep an eye on your aunts!

37:12.360 --> 37:12.840
No way.

37:12.920 --> 37:13.920
I need to help you.

37:14.230 --> 37:15.150
Really, you can't.

37:15.150 --> 37:15.610
This...

37:16.760 --> 37:18.000
Be careful!

37:18.230 --> 37:20.090
You don't deserve to be my father!

37:21.150 --> 37:22.350
Stop fighting! Stop!

37:23.000 --> 37:24.460
Everyone get out of my way!

37:25.010 --> 37:25.850
Move!

37:25.880 --> 37:26.630
Yong is here! Yong is here!

37:26.630 --> 37:27.290
Step aside!

37:33.320 --> 37:34.000
We're family.

37:34.000 --> 37:34.940
Xiaolan's uncle! Xiaolan's uncle!

37:34.940 --> 37:35.510
We're all family here.

37:35.510 --> 37:36.510
You bastard!

37:36.920 --> 37:38.230
I didn't come to your village to
get even with you,

37:38.230 --> 37:40.030
yet you dare come to our village?

37:40.280 --> 37:41.480
My sister marrying you was truly

37:41.480 --> 37:43.070
the worst luck imaginable!

37:44.070 --> 37:44.670
Yong,

37:45.360 --> 37:46.710
let's talk this through.

37:46.710 --> 37:47.510
Right, right.

37:47.590 --> 37:49.120
I have nothing to say to you!

37:51.110 --> 37:51.840
Xia Xiaolan,

37:52.190 --> 37:53.630
I'm asking you one last time!

37:53.630 --> 37:55.490
Are you coming back with me or not?

37:55.770 --> 37:56.190
You've never cared about me

37:56.190 --> 37:57.720
as your daughter deep down.

37:58.280 --> 38:00.190
If it weren't for my mom and my uncle,

38:00.190 --> 38:02.030
I would have died
in the Xia family long ago.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.760
Just pretend I'm already dead.

38:03.880 --> 38:05.030
I will absolutely never

38:05.030 --> 38:05.510
return to the Xia family.

38:05.510 --> 38:06.800
Did you hear what Xiaolan said?

38:06.800 --> 38:07.800
Did you hear that?

38:08.000 --> 38:09.670
You dare come to our village
to take people away?

38:09.670 --> 38:11.000
You think Qijing Village has no one
to stand up for itself?

38:11.000 --> 38:11.440
Is that it?

38:11.440 --> 38:11.980
That's right!

38:11.980 --> 38:13.190
Who do you think you are?

38:13.190 --> 38:14.400
Coming to our village causing trouble!

38:14.400 --> 38:14.840
Get out!

38:14.840 --> 38:17.800
Get out of here!

38:18.230 --> 38:19.150
Who do you think you are?

38:19.150 --> 38:20.230
Coming to cause trouble in our village!

38:20.230 --> 38:20.840
Scram!

38:21.030 --> 38:22.510
If I ever come looking for you again,

38:22.510 --> 38:23.840
I'm no better than a dog!

38:23.930 --> 38:26.890
Get lost! Get lost already!

38:26.920 --> 38:28.180
Get far away from here!

38:28.520 --> 38:29.150
What trash!

38:29.150 --> 38:29.800
We should have cut ties with them
completely.

38:29.800 --> 38:31.460
Our Ziyu is just too kind-hearted.

38:31.460 --> 38:31.990
Let's go.

38:35.670 --> 38:36.280
Xiaolan.

38:36.480 --> 38:37.840
Go back and tell Xia Ziyu...

38:37.840 --> 38:39.210
-Let's talk properly.
-I know exactly what happened

38:39.210 --> 38:40.860
between her and Wang Jianhua.

38:40.860 --> 38:41.710
I just don't want to

38:41.710 --> 38:42.590
waste my time

38:42.590 --> 38:43.630
on two worthless people.

38:43.630 --> 38:44.290
Yes, right.

38:44.310 --> 38:45.190
If she wants to make it big,

38:45.190 --> 38:46.250
I wish her success.

38:46.400 --> 38:47.400
Xiaolan, well...

38:47.480 --> 38:49.150
But if she ever dares to
act shamefully again,

38:49.150 --> 38:50.210
I won't let her off.

38:50.440 --> 38:51.360
No, she won't.

38:51.510 --> 38:52.000
And you.

38:53.110 --> 38:54.800
You were trying to help her stop me?

38:54.800 --> 38:55.510
Do you think if Xia Ziyu

38:55.510 --> 38:56.630
becomes successful,

38:56.630 --> 38:58.090
your family will benefit?

38:58.960 --> 39:00.690
You're just another blood bag.

39:00.920 --> 39:02.320
Without me and my mother,

39:02.470 --> 39:03.330
all the bad stuff

39:03.330 --> 39:04.590
will fall on your family.

39:04.590 --> 39:05.480
W-What blood bag?

39:05.480 --> 39:06.360
Blood... Blood?

39:06.360 --> 39:07.190
Well, Xiaolan's uncle,

39:07.190 --> 39:08.360
please don't keep holding that stick.

39:08.360 --> 39:08.800
Yeah,

39:08.800 --> 39:09.800
it's quite scary.

39:11.320 --> 39:12.650
You're already scared?

39:13.140 --> 39:13.590
I'm not.

39:13.590 --> 39:14.880
In the future, that old hag

39:14.880 --> 39:16.550
will be depending on you two.

39:16.800 --> 39:17.760
Your good days

39:17.760 --> 39:19.020
are still ahead of you.

39:19.190 --> 39:19.590
Well,

39:19.670 --> 39:20.280
Xiaolan,

39:20.360 --> 39:21.510
no matter what,

39:21.510 --> 39:22.640
I'm still your aunt,

39:22.920 --> 39:23.440
right?

39:23.710 --> 39:25.690
We came here to talk things through
with you.

39:25.690 --> 39:27.150
Yeah, we just wanted to
ask you to come back,

39:27.150 --> 39:27.590
right?

39:27.590 --> 39:29.590
Besides, our Ziyu is so kind.

39:29.590 --> 39:31.370
She won't hold a grudge against you.

39:31.370 --> 39:32.510
She's a college student after all.

39:32.510 --> 39:32.910
Right.

39:33.000 --> 39:35.290
So she's a college student.
What's the big deal?

39:35.290 --> 39:36.230
I'll get into college too

39:36.230 --> 39:37.030
and show you.

39:37.960 --> 39:39.020
Alright, Xiaolan.

39:39.150 --> 39:40.280
Go ahead and take the exam.

39:40.280 --> 39:41.840
I believe you'll definitely pass.

39:41.840 --> 39:42.280
What a load of nonsense.

39:42.280 --> 39:42.730
After you pass,

39:42.730 --> 39:43.590
this whole family will be yours.

39:43.590 --> 39:44.850
Go away. Just get lost!

39:45.630 --> 39:46.510
What trash!

39:46.510 --> 39:47.710
Get lost! Leave now!

39:52.960 --> 39:53.960
As my father,

39:54.710 --> 39:55.760
you never once tried

39:55.760 --> 39:57.820
to understand what really happened.

39:58.030 --> 39:58.840
When rumors were

39:58.840 --> 40:00.370
making my life unbearable,

40:00.550 --> 40:02.710
did you feel even
a bit of sympathy for me?

40:02.710 --> 40:03.840
After all this time,

40:03.920 --> 40:05.110
did you ever think of

40:05.230 --> 40:08.430
confronting Zhang Erlai
and settling the score with him?

40:13.490 --> 40:14.700
The rumor about Xiaolan

40:14.700 --> 40:15.830
dating Zhang Erlai—

40:15.930 --> 40:17.190
where did it come from?

40:18.190 --> 40:18.590
Well,

40:18.960 --> 40:20.150
how would I know?

40:20.680 --> 40:21.670
Someone said something,

40:21.670 --> 40:23.360
so the rumor started to spread.

40:23.360 --> 40:24.400
Besides, that Zhang Erlai

40:24.400 --> 40:25.870
admitted it himself, didn't he?

40:25.870 --> 40:27.400
If he hadn't done anything,

40:27.590 --> 40:28.990
would he have confessed?

40:29.070 --> 40:30.000
Sister-in-law,

40:30.070 --> 40:31.920
let's not discuss this on the street.

40:31.920 --> 40:33.760
It's not something to be proud of.

40:33.760 --> 40:35.280
Let's talk back at home, Dajun.

40:35.280 --> 40:35.720
Hey,

40:36.280 --> 40:37.280
he asked me.

40:37.280 --> 40:38.500
I wasn't the one who spread it.

40:38.500 --> 40:40.630
And you're saying
I'm doing something shameful?

40:40.630 --> 40:41.880
When did I say anything?

40:41.880 --> 40:43.800
Didn't you just mention Zhang Erlai?

40:43.800 --> 40:44.400
Well, I...

40:45.070 --> 40:45.590
Dajun,

40:46.000 --> 40:48.030
did you know Zhang Erlai was arrested?

40:48.030 --> 40:49.160
He can't escape now.

40:50.070 --> 40:51.440
Did he implicate

40:51.440 --> 40:52.150
Xiaolan?

40:52.440 --> 40:54.280
The police won't arrest Xiaolan,
will they?

40:54.280 --> 40:56.110
Zhang Erlai is charged with indecency.

40:56.110 --> 40:57.320
Why would the police arrest

40:57.320 --> 40:58.190
the victim?

40:59.840 --> 41:00.710
Sister-in-law,

41:00.710 --> 41:01.590
in these situations,

41:01.590 --> 41:02.480
women always suffer the most.

41:02.480 --> 41:04.000
Why would they arrest Xiaolan?

41:04.000 --> 41:05.200
You're really funny.

41:05.800 --> 41:07.330
Isn't that what I just said?

41:07.400 --> 41:08.590
That women suffer?

41:08.960 --> 41:09.960
Hey, you... Um...

41:10.800 --> 41:11.290
Dajun,

41:11.320 --> 41:13.230
I was just worried about

41:13.280 --> 41:14.110
our Xiaolan.

41:14.440 --> 41:16.150
Why are you giving me signals?

41:16.150 --> 41:17.590
Wait for me, Jingui!

41:24.590 --> 41:25.190
Xiaolan.

41:25.630 --> 41:26.850
Today, your father...

41:26.850 --> 41:28.160
Don't worry, Mom.

41:28.590 --> 41:29.320
Today, I embarrassed him

41:29.320 --> 41:30.070
in front of all those people

41:30.070 --> 41:31.330
and made him lose face,

41:31.480 --> 41:32.750
and he also made a harsh threat,

41:32.750 --> 41:34.070
saying he wouldn't come back again.

41:34.070 --> 41:34.630
I think

41:34.630 --> 41:35.460
we can have a few days

41:35.460 --> 41:36.260
of peace now.

41:37.150 --> 41:37.550
But...

41:38.150 --> 41:38.610
Well...

41:40.510 --> 41:41.040
Xiaolan,

41:41.320 --> 41:42.510
we can't keep going on like this.

41:42.510 --> 41:43.910
What do you suggest we do?

41:43.960 --> 41:45.670
Go back and continue to work like
beasts of burden,

41:45.670 --> 41:46.670
let them keep bullying us,

41:46.670 --> 41:47.190
spreading lies about me

41:47.190 --> 41:48.230
and ruining my reputation?

41:48.230 --> 41:48.590
No.

41:49.110 --> 41:50.590
That's not what I meant.

41:51.800 --> 41:52.840
I just feel that

41:55.070 --> 41:56.230
I'm useless.

41:57.150 --> 41:58.360
I failed protect you,

41:59.160 --> 42:00.810
and I even make you

42:00.840 --> 42:02.370
worry about me all the time.

42:05.000 --> 42:06.400
I'm just so worthless.

42:11.110 --> 42:11.630
Mom.

42:12.510 --> 42:13.880
Stop overthinking it.

42:14.440 --> 42:15.600
The two of us

42:15.630 --> 42:17.430
are depending on each other now.

42:17.670 --> 42:19.270
No one is protecting anyone.

42:19.630 --> 42:20.480
Besides,

42:20.760 --> 42:22.230
when I prepare for the exams later,

42:22.230 --> 42:23.000
I'll need you

42:23.030 --> 42:23.920
to support me.

42:27.000 --> 42:27.630
Xiaolan,

42:29.510 --> 42:31.110
I just heard from your uncle
that you want to take

42:31.110 --> 42:33.370
the college entrance exam. Is that true?

42:35.360 --> 42:36.320
Don't blame me

42:36.320 --> 42:37.720
for being discouraging.

42:38.110 --> 42:38.840
College

42:39.400 --> 42:40.660
isn't easy to get into.

42:40.920 --> 42:42.680
That Chen Qing from the Chief's family,

42:42.680 --> 42:43.480
his academic performance

42:43.480 --> 42:44.430
is among the best

42:44.590 --> 42:45.920
in our villages,

42:46.360 --> 42:48.010
yet he failed to
get into college last year.

42:48.010 --> 42:48.550
And this year,

42:48.550 --> 42:50.190
he's repeating at No.1 High School.

42:50.190 --> 42:52.590
Chen Qing happens to be
at No.1 High School?

42:52.760 --> 42:54.360
Then I'll ask him for information
tomorrow.

42:54.360 --> 42:54.880
Right.

42:55.150 --> 42:55.750
You should

42:55.880 --> 42:57.480
get more information first.

42:57.760 --> 42:58.550
Don't rush.

42:59.190 --> 42:59.550
Okay.

43:00.670 --> 43:01.820
Fen, you've had a long day.

43:01.820 --> 43:02.630
Get some rest.

43:02.800 --> 43:03.400
All right.

43:09.000 --> 43:09.440
Cheng.

43:09.800 --> 43:10.110
Wei.

43:10.280 --> 43:10.940
Zhou Cheng!

43:10.960 --> 43:12.690
There's a letter for you today.

43:15.760 --> 43:16.360
Thank you.

43:17.030 --> 43:17.630
I'm leaving.

43:17.630 --> 43:18.630
Be careful, Meng.

43:19.670 --> 43:20.190
So?

43:20.440 --> 43:21.400
Is it from Xiaolan?
